34","tid":1927254,"uid":307619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4bcf2c867d559a12c9d67c2b785e37ed40e87142","tid":1927254,"uid":5205,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"12550524f8fd0e8af2638d926439763998fa484e","tid":1927254,"uid":307619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"79de71388d039e4d5ea70990d8cd5772203384c1","tid":1927254,"uid":5205,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-15T18:17:19.000Z","msg":"講真 毒撚 無朋友無愛情<br />\n屋企人係藍<br />\n感覺自己智力唔高又無大志"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-15T18:25:26.000Z","msg":"唔好阿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-15T18:36:26.000Z","msg":"由細到大 搵人傾計都係係1對1 1對多就盡量唔出聲"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-15T18:40:25.000Z","msg":"我都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e305024adc3c61cb566160e65d0a8e9eadcf9991","tid":1927254,"uid":5205,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"6701c7b3cf344874d9ed985b4b8d8e8241ca7e34","tid":1927254,"uid":307619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4bcf2c867d559a12c9d67c2b785e37ed40e87142","tid":1927254,"uid":5205,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"12550524f8fd0e8af2638d926439763998fa484e","tid":1927254,"uid":307619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-15T18:25:26.000Z","msg":"唔好阿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-15T18:36:26.000Z","msg":"由細到大 搵人傾計都係係1對1 1對多就盡量唔出聲"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-15T18:40:25.000Z","msg":"我都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-15T18:46:34.000Z","msg":"心態已經像個死人"},{"pid":"45ab66f685a3ff1910d69049c4586b8cd455af02","tid":1927254,"uid":223428,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T15:18:59.000Z","msg":"會好辛苦。<br />\n你有意識就會閉氣，閉氣就會恐慌，恐慌就會亂郁，用走更多氧氣。<br />\n然後你一暈就會嗆水，但一開始你的喉嚨會自動封實你條氣管，有時仲會封到心跳停止為止。<br />\n水一入肺的話，海水會將細胞入面的水份抽入肺泡嚟摧毀你個肺，引發炎症同缺氧，所以你專登索水落去都會好痛苦。<br />\n仲有，你塊面一掂到凍水，你的身體就會有個本能去降低心率同往末梢的血流，降低耗氧量，即係話你會死得比較慢。<br />\n<br />\n（我都好孤獨，父母半藍，IQ未夠100，性格懦弱，有朋友但不會出街。但我未自殺。神將生命比我同你，一定有我們未知的理由）"},{"pid":"49336ece49e4eae094ebcf6a992525d7c23b333d","tid":1927254,"uid":88006,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T15:32:47.000Z","msg":"其實冇問題架喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n做人唔係玩thesims 唔一定要有幾多個朋友<br />\n唔一定要做party queen 唔一定要做其他人做緊嘅野"},{"pid":"8b362c5a026bf30f6b66b7c9ced84c963f85b70e","tid":1927254,"uid":140309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4bcf2c867d559a12c9d67c2b785e37ed40e87142","tid":1927254,"uid":5205,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"12550524f8fd0e8af2638d926439763998fa484e","tid":1927254,"uid":307619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"79de71388d039e4d5ea70990d8cd5772203384c1","tid":1927254,"uid":5205,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-15T18:17:19.000Z","msg":"講真 毒撚 無朋友無愛情<br />\n屋企人係藍<br />\n感覺自己智力唔高又無大志"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-15T18:25:26.000Z","msg":"唔好阿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-15T18:36:26.000Z","msg":"由細到大 搵人傾計都係係1對1 1對多就盡量唔出聲"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T21:14:30.000Z","msg":"傾咩計先，傾心事不嬲都係對信得過嘅人講㗎啦，1對1好平常<br />\n<br />\n求其搵個人傾下政治議題囉，宜家最易吹水嘅話題黎，我自己本身都無乜野講好抑鬱，但一講到社會政治議題就好多野想同人講，愈講就愈調整到心態，所以6月起多咗機會同人講野，情況改善咗唔少"},{"pid":"819c582e1b3a01cd8fe14f61b8555dc82f97c361","tid":1927254,"uid":99299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T17:15:28.000Z","msg":"絲打 feel 到你好似得自己一個咁 冇咩朋友可以傾下計 屋企人又唔同立場 冇計傾 呢段時間一定好辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但你要記住香港仲有好多同路人同你一齊同行架 有事可以拎出嚟大家一齊傾架"},{"pid":"7a8e0604d1c36f2dad7d0abc2782ddb086ffbed9","tid":1927254,"uid":58316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T17:18:08.000Z","msg":"跳海=/=蹈海"},{"pid":"ebaa78b3c114e02856461ff3b851cda43839e232","tid":1927254,"uid":88663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T17:19:15.000Z","msg":"睇字都feel到你沮喪"},{"pid":"629428bb138e81c327bc16a940ef0e6026e293fc","tid":1927254,"uid":34777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T17:22:44.000Z","msg":"唔係<br />\n2樣都好辛苦<br />\n睇你打字都感受到你承受好大壓力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不如一齊傾下?<br />\n呢度好多同路人等緊你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}